# Walkthrough - Sakakibara Tax Accountant Office Website

## Summary
I have successfully created the top page (first view) for Sakakibara Tax Accountant Office. The design follows the "Japanese Corporate" aesthetic with the specified color scheme.

## Implementation Details
- **HTML**: Semantic HTML5 structure with BEM-style classes.
- **CSS**: Responsive design using CSS variables for easy maintenance.
- **Visuals**: Custom generated hero image denoting professionalism.

## Verification
I have verified the website layout on both desktop and mobile resolutions.

### Desktop View
The desktop view features a transparent sticky header and a large hero section.
![Desktop View](/brain/49cacb16-cfd0-4e20-98b8-cc94fc8ab517/desktop_view_1768334035034.png)

### Mobile View (Responsive)
The mobile view adapts the layout, stacking elements and using a hamburger menu (visual only for this demo).
![Mobile View](/brain/49cacb16-cfd0-4e20-98b8-cc94fc8ab517/mobile_view_1768334063401.png)

## Next Steps
- Verify actual interaction of the mobile menu (JavaScript not yet implemented for toggle).
- Add more sections (Services, About, etc.) as needed.
